  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1324954/" class="title-link">五忘于江湖</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1324954"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/1207019/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1207019-11.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/1207019/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">柏邦妮</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2008-03-13"
      class="main-meta">2008-03-13 02:38:32</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1324954_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  最近在读连阔如先生写的《江湖丛谈》。 是在飞机上一份小报上看见连载的其中一段，大感兴趣，回来买的。 是讲解放前江湖上各种门道里头的关关节节，门门道道， 举凡江湖规矩，算卦相面，挑方卖药，杂技戏法，保镖卖艺，评书流派，相声口技， 坑蒙拐骗，大鼓竹板……无一不谈。 ...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/1324954/#comments">(5回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">11有用 / 2没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_1324954_full" class="hidden">
